 ), LPJ-GUESS (Lund-Potsdam-Jena General Ecosystem Simulator) (
 
  59
 ), LPX (Land surface Processes and eXchanges) (
 
  60
 ), ORCHIDEE (Organizing Carbon and Hydrology in Dynamic Ecosystems) (
 
